This directory contains golden test files from external projects.

weather.avro, weather-deflate.avro, weather-snappy.avro, weather-zstd.avro:
  From the Apache Avro project (https://github.com/apache/avro),
  share/test/data/. Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

deflate-invalid-data.avro, snappy-invalid-crc.avro, snappy-invalid-data.avro,
snappy-short-crc.avro, zstd-invalid-data.avro:
  From the hamba/avro project (https://github.com/hamba/avro),
  ocf/testdata/. Licensed under the MIT License.
